The paper deals with a supervised classification problem and proposes an algorithm that combines active learning and imbalance-aware learning. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the application of the proposed algorithm is in protein function prediction, which involves analyzing and interpreting biological data, indicating a possible fit with the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision (cs.CV), and Computational Biology (cs.CR) sub-categories. The paper may also involve natural language processing, as it discusses protein function prediction benchmarks, which could place it in the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
